2017;;Donald Cried;;American;;Kristopher Avedisian;;Kristopher Avedisian (director/screenplay); Kristopher Avedisian, Jesse Wakeman, Louisa Krause, Ted Arcidi;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Donald_Cried;;A Manhattanite banker returns to his hometown to pick up an urn and forgets his wallet. He seeks help from a home across the street only to find that it is still occupied by his high school neighbor who holds him hostage.